Description

Dinosaurs and Volcanoes AIO has adorable dinos migrating across the plain with volcanoes, dino eggs, assorted foliage, and trees. This print would make even the littlest dino lover happy! Our  Dinosaurs and Volcanoes AIO is a stay Dry AIO, which has an inner of PUL and a Hemp Bamboo Organic Cotton soaker core topped with Athletic Wicking Jersey to create that stay dry feel.

This Dinosaurs and Volcanoes AIO diaper is Made-to-Order so please choose your inner PUL color choice and snaps from the drop down menu. The main product photo is the best possible PUL, and snap color combinations for this AIO diaper.

Turnaround time for this Made-to-Order AIO diaper is about 3-4 weeks. Please be comfortable with this wait before ordering. Thank you!!

Why you’ll love this Dinosaurs and Volcanoes AIO Diaper:

  • Easy to Clean and Quick to Dry
  • Stay Dry Wicking Jersey Topped inner soaker layer
  • 7 Layers of Hemp Bamboo Organic Cotton
  • Premium Quality Elastics
  • Reinforced PolyResin Snaps
  • 5 Waist Positions for Longer Use
  • 3 Rise Positions
  • Front & Back Attached Petals
  • No Cover Needed
  • Soakers Agitate Out in Wash

How to care for your Dinosaurs and Volcanoes AIO Diaper:

  1. Dump Solids
  2. Cold  Quick Wash Cycle
  3. Hot Wash Cycle
  4. Cloth Diaper Safe Detergent
    • Ointments Ok with Liner
  5. Machine Dry Medium or Hang Dry
    • No Bleach/Fabric Softener or Iron

Dinosaurs and Volcanoes AIO Diaper Materials:

  • Inner: 100% Polyester Knit
  • Outer: 73% Polyester / 27% Polyurethane
  • Soakers: 40% Hemp 30% Bamboo 30% Certified Organic Cotton
